    Strategy for resolving the requested media types for a ServerWebExchange.

    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev

    • 方法详细资料

      • resolveMediaTypes

        List<org.springframework.http.MediaType> resolveMediaTypes(org.springframework.web.server.ServerWebExchange exchange)
                                                    throws org.springframework.web.server.NotAcceptableStatusException
        Resolve the given request to a list of requested media types. The returned list is ordered by specificity first and by quality parameter second.
        参数:
        exchange - the current exchange
        返回:
        the requested media types or an empty list
        抛出:
        org.springframework.web.server.NotAcceptableStatusException - if the requested media types is invalid
